channel.title: Come on my new forums! (link approved by mopar)
channel.description:
Yeah, I'll probably get flamed for this...but still...
Everyone come on my new forums!
I'm trying to get them more popular, right now we have 73 posts total and 66 members =\
I check these forums like every single minute and will do my best to do whatever suits you.
Link: [url=http://www.forumspring.com/rs2ps/index.php?]The forums[/url]
There is a website, but it's awful...if someone can help me with that add me on msn...I'll pay...
Also, I'm looking for moderators for the forum. I look for active people mostly. Since we have like 2 people with over 5 posts right now...
Any more reasons? Do you need more? Just click the link and post...not that hard...If this post dies, the link is also in my sig. I'll stop talking now.
